33.
2235Parittārammaṇo dhammo parittārammaṇassa dhammassa vipākapaccayena paccayo…  āhārapaccayena paccayo…  indriyapaccayena paccayo…  jhānapaccayena paccayo…  maggapaccayena paccayo…  sampayuttapaccayena paccaya…  atthipaccayena paccayo…  natthipaccayena paccayo…  vigatapaccayena paccaya…  avigatapaccayena paccayo.
